1
00:00:00,000 --> 00:00:04,000
What if I told you pH isn't just a number?

2
00:00:04,000 --> 00:00:06,800
pH tracks hydrogen ion activity in solutions.

3
00:00:06,800 --> 00:00:09,200
Acids donate, bases accept these ions.

4
00:00:09,200 --> 00:00:14,400
But did you know this affects everything from soil to our own bodies?

5
00:00:14,400 --> 00:00:18,400
A pH below 7 means more hydrogen ions, indicating acidity.

6
00:00:18,400 --> 00:00:20,800
Above 7, it’s basic—more hydroxide ions.

7
00:00:20,800 --> 00:00:27,200
So, next time you check pH, remember it’s more than a scale—it’s a balance of ions.

8
00:00:27,200 --> 00:00:29,200
Curious about more science mysteries?

9
00:00:29,200 --> 00:00:30,800
Hit follow for more!
